  <SourceScript>k__BackingField: "Narration: That\u2019s\u2026 the end of the day.\r\n\r\nNarration:
    And\u2026 you have enough money to buy your name back.\r\n\r\nNarration: Wow.\r\n\r\nNarration:
    You didn\u2019t think you\u2019d be able to do it.\r\n\r\nNarration: \u2026I
    mean part of the money you\u2019ve gotten is also going back to paying off for
    this pretty cool caravan.\r\n\r\nNarration: But regardless. \r\n\r\nNarration:
    You did it.\r\n\r\nNarration: It feels a bit bittersweet, honestly.\r\n\r\nNarration:
    You met a lot of nice people, but\u2026\r\n\r\nNarration: At least you\u2019ll
    be able to go back to your solitude, you suppose.\n\nNarration: ...\r\n\r\nNarration:
    \u2026time to pack up shop.\r\n"
